Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friday the 13th...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On this day, a man met his fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,FBI investigator, Akai Shuuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:19.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A while ago, the FBI stopped the assassination of Domon\NYasutera that had been plotted by the Black Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:23.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,They also captured one of the organization's\Nmembers, anchorwoman Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:28.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,In actually, she was a spy from the CIA\Nthat had infiltrated the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We tricked the organization into seizing Mizunashi Rena back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And successfully placed her back within the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, in order to prove her loyalty to the organization,\NMizunashi Rena was ordered to gun down Akai Shuuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, after he was called out to Raiha Pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think you'd go this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That it's worked out... {\alpha&HFF&\t(2000,2001,\alpha&H00&)}this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, the FBI has driven into the organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A wedge of steel so deep that it can never be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All at the price of leaving a traumatic wound in their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.90,0:01:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is magic, attack the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On Saturday nights, be sure to click on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Detective Boys versus a robber group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI's also involved in a bank panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please give me a break, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm already past the age of celebrating birthdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be a killjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's going to have one light drink, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about, Camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the investigation into the organization dragging along...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just using this as an excuse to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, James is treating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, we need to choose a good alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, nothing too expensive, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Organization has activated a new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An agent who is frighteningly skilled at intelligence\Ngathering as well as observation and discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their codename is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we got information on him from that\NMizunashi Rena who managed to re-infiltrate the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he hasn't shown himself at all, that detective-like fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bourbon's target is likely that little girl known as "Sherry."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Based on everything that's transpired so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:05:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be surprising for the organization to think\Nthat little girl is connected to us FBI members.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that, we thought they would\Nmake a move and approach us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A while ago, the same type of listening bug used by that girl was\Ndeployed to lure the organization to Detective Mouri's agency...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we FBI ending up sniping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although, the one who planted the bug\Nwas actually Edogawa Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, that person liked that alcohol too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who shot those guys that'd been\Nlured to a building 700 yards away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} too, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was as you said, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} were here, we wouldn't have to fear that Bourbon guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't fear him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're just waiting for the organization to\Nbecome impatient and make a move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, Akai Shuuichi is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do not bring his name up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do be more considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To her, Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} wasn't merely an FBI colleague, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two started going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she's the one you mentioned before, the\Nmember of that syndicate, Miyano Akemi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we have to break this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're only going out with her because of the investigation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see the need for us to separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an organization I must crush,\Neven if it requires sacrificing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being able to love two women at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That just isn't who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To have had the{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce to work with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you, all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SHUU!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it, that was Shuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he should be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be a doppelganger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to meet him and make sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember parking my car around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you saw someone from the organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just lost my way, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That aside, did you get some good alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I couldn't use my card at that store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I didn't bring that much yen with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, but could you pay for us first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I planned to make a withdrawal later, so my wallet's empty now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll make a trip to a nearby bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait for me at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it has to be someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just an illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Shuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you saved all of your New Year's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I opened my very own account a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got quite a lot and you're saving it all, isn't that a waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please call it being thrifty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, what did you do with your New Year's money then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave it to Mom for safekeeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she'll use it to buy expensive stuff for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did she buy anything for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'd say, "Don't be extravagant."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's pretty clever, Genta's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, she could be saving up just in case Genta becomes terribly sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's the same as saving with a bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm gonna get back everything I've received so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I won't get sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oww! My stomach hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you eat something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:10:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only had two helpings of curry rice for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I went to pick you up, I saw\Nsoy flour on your mouth, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because, after eating curry,\NI felt like eating something sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I roasted some mochi from the fridge, made\Nsome kinako mochi and ate four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I felt like eating something spicy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I put soy sauce on them, wrapped them\Nwith dried seaweed, and ate three more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just ate too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll buy some stomach medicine from a nearby pharmacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you need to in the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His New Year's money will end up as his food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sums it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't notice us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she had something on her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, ma'am, please avoid using your cellphone while using the ATM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're doing our best to prevent cases of remittance fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cellphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both your and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s prints are there on the cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As are the prints of the man whose burnt\Ncorpse was found just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's dead... haven't I told myself that numerous times?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To have seen such an illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope it doesn't happen again... I don't want to experience that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's as though a bullet just penetrated my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lock the entrances and close the shutters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone gather in one place now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sound just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko and Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll check out the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up and have a seat over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see how it is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna get hurt, get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's someone you know or brought along, stay close to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay close to someone you know or brought along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's been locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't look so normal inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shutters are closing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bank robbery, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the time being, put your cellphones in this bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sort of thing happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, during that bus-jacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, foreign lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't understand Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I understand a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then hand over your cellphone and sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Shuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Shuu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say that you're Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Burn marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, he managed to escape from the burning Chevrolet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the shocking experience robbed him of his voice and memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop making a fuss, you foreign woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and put your cellphone in this bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you too, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastard, you wanna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He no talk because a shock from accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The burn marks, they proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he no talk even if had phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just sit down and hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I have to take him back to the FBI and restore his memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to know how he survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And whose burnt body was in the Chevrolet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But first, I have to take care of these robbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is the branch chief here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good, come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared, just pack all your money into these cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Easy, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems like you'd know about where the money is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, the ones who have no companions here, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here and take a roll of tape each!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use it to tape the eyes and mouths of everyone with\Na companion, and tie their arms behind their backs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you aren't acquainted with any of them,\NI don't have to worry about you going soft on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, we'll tape you up all the same afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:16:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm putting it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me go potty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I no hold it more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's that foreign woman again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pwetty pwease!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, but your eyes, mouth and arms need to be taped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Walk faster now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, won't make a difference to just take her to the men's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like there's anyone here to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me when you finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, with your arms bound,\Nyou can't get your underwear off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll do the honors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of an FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We originally came with Mitsuhiko to make a deposit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ended up bringing Genta to the restroom due to his stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we heard a loud bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been hiding in here ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My stomach has already calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many robbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five, and all of them are armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they're after the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:19:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they ordered the money to be packed inside their cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's strange, they sorted out the ones with companions...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And allowed only the branch chief to pack the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, all of them were concerned with the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt I can do this, but if I can defeat them alone, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Jodie, the game starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't need to go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking something may have gone\Nwrong here, and it turns out I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No use, he's completely out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a drag carrying him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just take off his mask and jacket, and seat him on the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll appear to be a customer who was hiding in the restroom\Nand got beaten by the robbers when they found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, carry that end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, who was that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, no need to know who she is or where she's from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll just blast off anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} was taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to beat those punks up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there are five of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there are four.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really bad, something really bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've completely surrounded the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have the robbers listed their demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not yet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this situation, it would be normal for robbers\Nto use hostages as a shield to flee the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but I think they'll just\Ngive up and surrender soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They have no way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw the inside before the shutters went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw several men with guns and masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to pull it off wearing those...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd have to arm up in a large vehicle,\Npark it in front of the bank, and charge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They planned their robbery, but they\Ndidn't escape after stealing the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead they closed everyone inside without\Nmaking a demand, isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They probably have something up their sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A plan to take the money and get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a sly fox she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something as unworthy as a bank robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will only end up ruining your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said there wasn't much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.38,0:24:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, why didn't he keep his mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside of those cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There may be bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bombs!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.91,0:24:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hostages
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.76,0:24:55.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Look forward to the Next Episode
